---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'About';
const description = 'About your blog.';
const permalink = `${Astro.site.href}about`;
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} permalink={permalink} current="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <figure class="about-image">
      <img src="../assets/hacker1.webp" alt="Illustration of a notebook" width="330">
      <figcaption>
        Illustration by Gemini
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
    <p>Hi there! 👋</p>

    <p>I'm <strong>Jeya Seelan</strong>, a <strong>Security Engineer & Researcher</strong> with 4+ years of experience in <strong>Penetration testing, Red teaming, Security Research and Security automation</strong>.</p>

    <p>🔍 I Specialize in <strong>Web, Network, and Infra security assessments</strong>, along with <strong>bug bounty hunting</strong> and <strong>CTF challenges</strong>.</p>

    <p>🚀 Passionate about <strong>breaking and securing systems</strong>, I love uncovering vulnerabilities and strengthening defenses.</p>

    <p>💬 Always open to discussing <strong>offensive security, red teaming, and security engineering</strong>—feel free to connect!</p>

    <p>📬 <strong>Let's chat!</strong> Reach out on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jeyaseelans/">LinkedIn</a> or  <a href="https://x.com/rootxjs">Twitter</a> or <a href="https://github.com/rootxjs">GitHub</a>.</p>

    <p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-image {
    float: right;
    margin: -3em -7em 2em 2em;
    max-width: 300px;
  }

  .about-image img {
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1020px) {
    .about-image {
      float: none;
      margin: 0 auto 2em;
    }
  }
</style>
